Mushroom Tacos

25 min
$10
350 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 4

Dietary Tags:

vegetariangluten-free

Cuisine:

Mexican

Course:

Main

Tags:

tacoeasyquickvegetarian

Description

Delicious tacos filled with sautéed mushrooms, topped with fresh veggies and zesty flavors.

Ingredients

  • corn tortillas: 8
  • cremini mushrooms: 2 cups
  • bell pepper: 1
  • red onion: 1 small
  • avocado: 1
  • fresh cilantro: 1/4 cup
  • lime: 1
  • olive oil: 1 tablespoon
  • salt: to taste
  • black pepper: to taste
  • cumin: 1 teaspoon
  • chili powder: 1 teaspoon
